{
  "text": "The variables \u0394H sol , \u0394S sol , \u0394G sol , %\u03b6 H and %\u03b6 TS were calculated from equations (4.4) to (4.13) and summarized in tables 5 and 6. \u0394H sol and \u0394G sol in pure and binary solvents are all positive, indicating that the dissolution process of DCBNT in all tested solvents is endothermic [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
